## Risks

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| Infinite loops from circular rules | High | Medium | Depth limit + cycle detection |
| Performance degradation with many rules | Medium | Medium | Debouncing, optimize matching |
| Complex UI confusing users | Medium | High | Start simple, add complexity gradually |
| Rules breaking after schema changes | Medium | Low | Version rules, migration system |
| Delayed actions lost on page reload | Medium | High | Document limitation, add persistence in P2 |

